ersea to outer space and into cyberspace our core capabilitiescyber northrop grumman has been battling cyber threats for more than  years and through aggressive technology investments in key research areas such as identity management situational awareness modeling and simulation cloud security and supply chain has a deep understanding of the breadth and complexity of cyber it is embedded in everything we do more  our core capabilitieslogistics and modernization northrop grumman is a leading provider of logistics solutions supporting the full lifecycle of platforms and systems for global defense and federalcivil customers delivering innovative technologydriven solutions and services to enable costeffective improvements for customer mission effectiveness more  our core capabilitiesautonomous systems northrop grumman is a premier provider of autonomous systems on land at sea in the air and in space these unmanned aircraft satellites and space systems and advanced technologies are critical to our national security autonomous systems operate in areas and environments where manned vehicles cannot allowing for prolonged missions and helping reduce risk to human lives more  our core capabilitiescisr northrop grumman is a leading provider of cisr systems that are the backbone of operations and of decision making our systems provide situational awareness from planning to execution we deliver analysis systems through to advanced communications payloads and integrated solutions that support the us and allied forces across the globe more  our core capabilities strike as a leader in integrated strike systems northrop grumman brings worldclass capabilities in system design systems engineering manufacturing and sustainment the ability to project power strategically anywhere in the world is an essential tenet of the us military our platforms like the b spirit stealth bomber and the bomber for the future the b raider provide a powerful projection of force more  our people and culture with more than  employees in all  states and in more than  countries we strive to attract and retain the best employees by providing an inclusive work environment wherein employees are receptive to diverse ideas perspectives and talents to help solve our toughest customer challenges to develop and maintain some of the most technically sophisticated products programs and services in the world learn more about our career opportunities • students and new grads • experienced professionals • military and veterans there is a new spirit of success in the company — and it is translating into a flow of innovative ideas that reminds me every day how humbling it is to work with such an amazing group of peoplewes bushchairman chief executive officer and presidentnorthrop grumman corporation our heritage our story is the successful integration of nearly  marquee companies developing groundbreaking innovations – such as the flying wing and the b spirit stealth bomber – while also achieving numerous historic accomplishments – from transporting charles lindbergh across the atlantic to carrying astronauts to the moons surface and back making history is what we do learn more about our heritage  what do marilyn monroe star trek and the mars rovers all have in common about northrop grumman your browser does not support iframes our values the women and men of northrop grumman corporation are guided by our values they describe our company as we want it to be we want our decisions and actions to demonstrate these values we believe that putting our values into practice creates longterm benefits for shareholders customers employees suppliers and the communities we serve learn more about our values  our responsibility at northrop grumman we are committed to maintaining the highest of ethical standards embracing diversity and inclusion protecting the environment and striving to be an ideal corporate citizen in the community and in the world learn more about our responsibility  northrop grumm